title: UNMA Electoral Overview in Eastern Region, Afghanistan, 2009
name: UNMA Electoral Overview in Eastern Region, Afghanistan, 2009
description:
The United Nations Assistance Mission in Afghanistan publishes an electoral overview of Afghanistan in the eastern region provinces: Nangarhar, Laghman, Kunar, and Nuristan.  

This dataset includes the number of polling centers in the eastern region, province number of districts, current and previous estimated number of closed polling centers, and number of voters in 2005 and 2009.

author.source: United Nations Assistance Mission in Afghanistan
